The Achoo! scripts work with you to produce a fast installation of Arch Linux
with a desktop environment and a greeter. These scripts are shared in the
spirit of the community, subject to the terms set out in the GNU GENERAL LICENSE.

How to use it:

1) You should be running a live Arch session (as 'root') with a working internet connection

2) First update the package list and install git: pacman -Sy git

3) Next get the scripts from Github: git clone git://github.com/Angeltoast/achoo

4) Then run it: cd achoo && ./achoo
